{"root":{"data":{"id":"dbsoehii4wo0","created":1754212413437,"text":"基于在线评论的产品评价与用户需求挖掘方法研究"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbsogjtcd400","created":1754212575174,"text":"考虑多阶段在线评论的产品评价方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdv59nowcg0","created":1756364197918,"text":"概念定义","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdv5395l2w0","created":1756364183978,"text":"多阶段在线评论"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdv57t0r5c0","created":1756364193887,"text":"why"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdw9xahiag0","created":1756367383929,"text":"传统的基于在线评论的产品评价方法多存在一个重要局限：静态化处理在线评论，即把所有时间、不同类型的在线评论混为一谈，这样的做法忽略了在线评论的“动态性”与“阶段性”。而在实际应用中，在线评论会随着产品生命周期、用户使用过程出现阶段性的差异。因此，为了更为准确提升产品评价的准确性，本研究采用多阶段的在线评论。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcelaz1jwx40","created":1756437993854,"text":"what"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcelb1nth680","created":1756437999554,"text":"包括产品使用前的提问评论文本、产品使用后的口碑评论文本、质量反馈评论文本。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcdv5gril1c0","created":1756364213387,"text":"产品评价","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdv5s7kcug0","created":1756364238302,"text":"企业以用户生成的在线评论为数据源，通过提取评论中的产品属性、量化用户对属性的情感倾向，分析产品属性情感倾向对用户满意度的影响，使用适用于多阶段在线评论的产品评价模型，确定产品在不同维度（属性、使用场景）的优劣势，为资源有限的产品研发与提升提供决策支持。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcell3ziwx40","created":1756438788257,"text":"方法步骤"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcemfzj31ls0","created":1756441207845,"text":"多阶段在线评论处理","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcelv1jhbnk0","created":1756439566575,"text":"提问评论"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcem0oyeoaw0","created":1756440009364,"text":"用车提问（只有问题，没有回答）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcembd2zaqg0","created":1756440845525,"text":"判断文本评论所表达的产品属性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcem14ppg2o0","created":1756440043667,"text":"配置提问（只有问题，没有回答）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcembs300io0","created":1756440878178,"text":"判断文本评论所表达的产品属性"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dceluhb52io0","created":1756439522535,"text":"口碑评论","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcelqp3e2pk0","created":1756439226024,"text":"判断分句后的文本评论表达的产品属性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dcelquu4kns0","created":1756439238525,"text":"计算产品属性所在文本评论的情感倾向"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dcelr44g2qo0","created":1756439258740,"text":"计算属性情感倾向与属性评分的关联系数（通过构建神经网络得到）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcem3g05pj40","created":1756440224972,"text":"质量反馈评论"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcem47hf3eg0","created":1756440284788,"text":"判断分句后的文本评论表达的产品属性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dcemdtho7vk0","created":1756441037970,"text":"计算产品属性所在文本评论的情感倾向"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcemgi1r25s0","created":1756441248156,"text":"产品评价计算"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcemgwpgzgg0","created":1756441280065,"text":"KANO计算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dcemh4yamw80","created":1756441298013,"text":"IPCA计算"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbsoi7tte9s0","created":1754212705809,"text":"考虑多角色用户评价的产品评价方法","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":-23.74999893829238},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdxr3ttt1s0","created":1756371551460,"text":"概念定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdxs8b3w6g0","created":1756371639576,"text":"多角色用户评价","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcep3xc2teo0","created":1756448726027,"text":"why","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcep42jf8y00","created":1756448737355,"text":" "},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcep3skbbdk0","created":1756448715642,"text":"what","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcekvqhd8k80","created":1756436799757,"text":"基于产品使用过程中不同使用需求、体验视角下的用户角色，从对应角色的在线评论中提取针对产品核心属性的评价，最终形成能够反映多角色组合下的综合评价体系。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcdxsogfa3k0","created":1756371674726,"text":"产品评价"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdxss4l7gw0","created":1756371682717,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcdvpc5j23k0","created":1756365770633,"text":"研究路线"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcdvpj7ki680","created":1756365785994,"text":"以”考虑多阶段在线评论的产品评价方法“中的产品评价为参数，构建多产品竞争仿真模型。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dcdxq5qmsjc0","created":1756371477256,"text":"方法步骤"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbsogmejf6w0","created":1754212580809,"text":"考虑产品评价的用户需求挖掘方法","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":6.249999720603455,"y":2.499999888241291}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcel3x53pj40","created":1756437441166,"text":"概念定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcel3zteq3s0","created":1756437446989,"text":"需求挖掘"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dcel434hoew0","created":1756437454190,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}